碧昂丝在圣诞节中场表演前嘲笑 Netflix 的缓冲问题https://www.nme.com/news/music/beyonce-pokes-fun-at-netflixs-buffering-issues-ahead-of-christmas-day-halftime-performance-3824765?u tm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=碧昂丝-戳-netflixs-缓冲问题-圣诞节前半场表演Laura MolloyWed, 25 Dec 2024 07:46:29 +0000 Music NewsNewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3824765 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Beyonce.-CREDIT_-Kevin-Winter_Getty-Images-for-iHeartRadio.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Beyonce.-CREDIT_-Kevin-Winter_Getty-Images-for-iHeartRadio.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Beyonce.-CREDIT_-Kevin-Winter_Getty-Images-for-iHeartRadio-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Beyonce.-CREDIT_-Kevin-Winter_Getty-Images-for-iHeartRadio-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Beyonce.-CREDIT_-Kevin-Winter_Getty-Images-for-iHeartRadio-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Beyonce.-CREDIT_-Kevin-Winter_Getty-Images-for-iHeartRadio-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Beyonce.-CREDIT_-Kevin-Winter_Getty-Images-for-iHeartRadio-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这是她今年的第一场演出，演出后只能在几个小时内进行直播</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/beyonce-pokes-fun-at-netflixs-buffering-issues-ahead-of-christmas-day-halftime-performance-3824765">碧昂丝在圣诞节中场表演前调侃 Netflix 缓冲问题的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Beyonce.-CREDIT_-Kevin-Winter_Getty-Images-for-iHeartRadio.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Beyonce.-CREDIT_-Kevin-Winter_Getty-Images-for-iHeartRadio.jpg 2000w, https://www